      <description>&lt;p&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;lead text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400 !mb-9 text-xl&#34;&gt;
  A novel brain-inspired architecture that introduces the concept of &amp;ldquo;temporality&amp;rdquo; to existing time-agnostic neuron models, giving rise to a series of brain-like emergent phenomena.
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;


&lt;h2 class=&#34;relative group&#34;&gt;Preface 
    &lt;div id=&#34;preface&#34; class=&#34;anchor&#34;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
    
    &lt;span
